original: Barrholm, Gustaf Artur, kamrer, Kinna, f. 24/1/08 i Jönköp. G. 34 m. Siri Holmqvist. Barn: Ulla f. 35, Inger 41, Kerstin 45. — Genomg. Ne-dins handisk. 28 samt korresp :sk. Kassör v. Krönleins Bryggeri i Jönköp. 30i-33, kamr. v. Kinna Bryggeri A-B sed. 33. Kassör i Marks härads bef :utb :fören. sed. 37, dito i RPO avd. i Kinna. Hobbies: rodd o. fiske. Älvsb. bef :utb :förb. förtjiSM.
translated: Barrholm, Gustaf Artur, accountant, from Kinna, born on January 24, 1908 in Jönköping. Married in 1934 to Siri Holmqvist. Children: Ulla born in 1935, Inger born in 1941, Kerstin born in 1945. Graduated from Ne-din's handicraft school in 1928 and correspondence school. Treasurer at Krönleins Brewery in Jönköping from 1930-1933, accountant at Kinna Brewery AB since 1933. Treasurer in the Marks County educational association since 1937 and also in the RPO department in Kinna. Hobbies include rowing and fishing. Received a merit award from the Älvsborg County educational association.
